    # Write a function that returns True if the object q will fly, and False otherwise. 
# The object q will fly if it is balanced (a palindromic list) and the sum of its elements is less than or equal to the maximum possible weight w.

    if sum(q) > w:
        return False

    i, j = 0, len(q)-1
    while i<j:
